elements postcode postcode Element
postcode &postcode.purpose;
&postcode.synopsis.gen; Description
PostCode is a postal code (in the United States, a ZIP code) in an Address.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; In an Address, this element may inherit the verbatim qualities of an address.
&postcode.parents.gen; &postcode.children.gen;
